# AthleteOS SQL Checks

Use these queries for quick database validation during tournament QA, debugging, and regression checks.

> Replace placeholder values like:
> - `YOUR_TOURNAMENT_ID`
> - `YOUR_DIVISION_ID`
> - `YOUR_TOURNAMENT_SLUG`
> - `AFFECTED_TEAM_ID`

---

## 1. Find tournament by slug

```sql
select
  id,
  name,
  slug,
  is_public,
  status
from tournaments
where slug = 'YOUR_TOURNAMENT_SLUG';

